《'''Inside'''》是一款由獨立遊戲工作室[[Playdead|Playdead]]所開發及發行的[[平台遊戲|平台]][[益智遊戲|解謎]]及[[冒險遊戲|冒險遊戲]]。遊戲無論在主題及視覺上均類似同一公司的另一款作品《[[地獄邊境|地獄邊境]]》，玩家需扮演一名小男孩，在黑白色的遊戲環境中解決不同的難題，並同時避免在3D滾動時死亡。

《Inside》分別於2016年6月29日、7月7日和8月23日在Xbox One及Windows还有PlayStation 4上發行，iOS平台在2017年12月15日发行以及[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]在2018年6月28日发行。<ref name="NSandIOS"/>游戏在推出後幾乎獲得一致好評，有部份評論家甚至稱本作為《[[地獄邊境|地獄邊境]]》的優秀的[[精神續作|精神續作]]<ref name="CD_1" /><ref name="MP_1" /><ref name="CK_1" /><ref name="AW_2" />。

== 玩法 ==

《Inside》是款解謎遊戲，玩家需控制一名沒有名字並身穿紅色衣服的小男孩探索一個超現實的環境，而遊戲畫面主要是黑白色、[[偽三維|2.5D]]及利用一些濺出的顏色來突出部份環境。玩家能控制小男孩作出走路、跑、游泳、攀爬及使用物件等動作來進行遊戲，在遊戲中期小男孩更會獲得能力，能精神控制死屍並操縱他們以解決各種謎題<ref name="JR_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.usgamer.net/articles/inside-xbox-one-preview |title = Xbox One Inside is a Superlative Platform Puzzler |author = Jaz Rignall |date = 2016-06-13 |publisher = US Gamer |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160718152046/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/inside-xbox-one-preview |archive-date = 2016-07-18 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="MS_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/13/e3-2016-inside-is-super-limbo-in-the-best-possible-way |title = E3 2016: Inside is Super Limbo in the Best Possible Way |author = Marty Sliva |date = 2016-06-13 |publisher = US Gamer |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160708154743/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/13/e3-2016-inside-is-super-limbo-in-the-best-possible-way |archive-date = 2016-07-08 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。當玩家未能快速地解決部份謎題時，例如是被獵人以麻醉鏢擊中、被狗隻捕捉或吃掉、或因處於水下太長時間而溺水，玩家所操控的小男孩便會死亡。本作與《地獄邊境》同樣，小男孩在死亡時會出現令人感到可怕的動畫，之後遊戲便會在最近的儲存點重新進行<ref name="MS_1" />。在本作中，有部份場景具有隱藏房間且內含一個小型球體，玩家可以進入這些房間並關掉球體，而當所有球體在玩家的遊玩過程中被關掉時，便能解鎖遊戲中的備用結局<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/06/29/how-to-find-all-of-insides-hidden-rooms-lamps-and-the-alternate-ending.aspx |title = How To Find All Of Inside’s Hidden Rooms And The Alternate Ending |author = Kyle Hilliard |date = 2016-06-29 |publisher = Game Informer |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160712230202/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/06/29/how-to-find-all-of-insides-hidden-rooms-lamps-and-the-alternate-ending.aspx |archive-date = 2016-07-12 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

== 開發 ==

遊戲工作室[[Playdead|Playdead]]於2010年7月發行了黑白色的獨立遊戲《[[地獄邊境|地獄邊境]]》，獲得大量好評及超過一百萬的銷售量<ref name="PK_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.polygon.com/2014/6/9/5793998/inside-playdead-xbox-one-e3-2014 |title = Inside is the next game from Limbo creators Playdead Studios |author = Philip Kollar |date = 2014-06-09 |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160713002147/http://www.polygon.com/2014/6/9/5793998/inside-playdead-xbox-one-e3-2014 |archive-date = 2016-07-13 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="AG_2" />。在發行後的數個月，Playdead開展了第二個遊戲開發項目，並暫稱為「項目2（Project 2）」<ref name="SS_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/4/8731865/inside-delayed-playdead-xbox-one |title = Inside, upcoming game from Limbo developer Playdead, delayed past 'early 2015' |author = Samit Sarkar |date = 2015-06-04 |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160718133009/http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/4/8731865/inside-delayed-playdead-xbox-one |archive-date = 2016-07-18 |dead-url = no }}</ref>
<ref name="AG_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/10/28/limbo-follow-up-will-be-more-crazy |title = Limbo Follow-Up Will be "More Crazy" |author = Andrew Goldfarb |date = 2011-10-28 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801070718/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/10/28/limbo-follow-up-will-be-more-crazy |archive-date = 2016-08-01 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="AG_2">{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/07/27/limbo-follow-up-project-2-is-at-least-2-years-away |title = Limbo Follow-Up Project 2 is ‘At Least 2 Years Away’ |author = Andrew Goldfarb |date = 2012-07-27 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160811222118/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/07/27/limbo-follow-up-project-2-is-at-least-2-years-away |archive-date = 2016-08-11 |dead-url = no }}{{Cite web |url = http://www.doyo.cn/article/79977 |title = 地狱边境的下一部作品至少两年之后才会面世_逗游网 |author = 宸恺 |date = 2012-07-27 |publisher = 逗游网 |language = zh-Hans |accessdate = 2017-01-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170202005709/http://www.doyo.cn/article/79977 |archive-date = 2017-02-02 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。作為《地獄邊境》的精神續作<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/95064/e3-2016-inside-preview-unsettling-feelings |title = E3 2016: Inside Preview: Unsettling Feelings |author = Steve Watts |date = 2016-06-13 |publisher = Shack News |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160718102025/http://www.shacknews.com/article/95064/e3-2016-inside-preview-unsettling-feelings |archive-date = 2016-07-18 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，雖然本作與《地獄邊境》十分相似，但本作更為「瘋狂」、「怪異」及3D<ref name="AG_1" />。此外，丹麥電影協會亦提供部分資金作遊戲開發用途<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://filmschoolrejects.com/inside-video-game-cinematic-storytelling-1e80324e10c8#.snt361psd |title = The Cinema Inside: How the video game Inside is a better movie than most movies. |author = Colton Ledford |date = 2016-07-08 |publisher = Film School Rejects |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-date = 2019-02-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190216180129/https://filmschoolrejects.com/inside-video-game-cinematic-storytelling-1e80324e10c8/#.snt361psd |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

雖然Playdead已經為《地獄邊境》建立了一個自定義的遊戲引擎，但最後他們選擇使用[[Unity_(遊戲引擎)|Unity]]為本作的遊戲引擎，以減輕工作量<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/126729/Limbo_Developer_Playdead_Using_Unity_Engine_For_Next_Title.php |title = Limbo Developer Playdead Using Unity Engine For Next Title |author = Mike Rose |date = 2011-08-25 |publisher = Gamasutra |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801185557/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/126729/Limbo_Developer_Playdead_Using_Unity_Engine_For_Next_Title.php |archive-date = 2016-08-01 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="AG_2" />。遊戲開發團隊為Unity遊戲引擎建立了{{tsl|en|Temporal anti-aliasing|時間混疊反鋸齒過濾器}}，以為本作創建具標誌性的外觀<ref name="AW_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/268722/Limbo_dev_opensources_its_Unity_5_antialiasing_tech.php |title = Limbo dev open-sources its Unity 5 anti-aliasing tech |author = Alex Wawro |date = 2016-03-22 |publisher = Gamasutra |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160721010539/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/268722/Limbo_dev_opensources_its_Unity_5_antialiasing_tech.php |archive-date = 2016-07-21 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2016年3月，Playdead在常見開源協議下發布了過濾器<ref name="AW_1" />。

與《地獄邊境》同樣，本作的音效由馬丁·斯蒂格·安德森負責。安德森受20世紀80年代的B級恐怖電影所影響，經常使用合成音樂，但他卻不想於本作使用合成音樂。相反，安德森利用真正的人頭骨來創造骨傳導的聲音，並在頭骨上接駁音頻轉換器和接觸式麥克風，以聲音合成來還原這些聲音，最終創造遊戲的音樂<ref name="JB_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.develop-online.net/interview/heard-about-how-playdead-used-a-real-human-skull-for-inside-s-audio/0209170 |title = Heard About: How Playdead used a real human skull for Inside's audio |author = John Broomhall |date = 2015-07-23 |publisher = Develop |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160702132131/http://www.develop-online.net/interview/heard-about-how-playdead-used-a-real-human-skull-for-inside-s-audio/0209170 |archive-date = 2016-07-02 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。本作的遊戲玩法及音樂都具有更緊密的整合，在部份謎題上音樂更能配合遊戲畫面。這需要安德森在相比進行《地獄邊境》的音樂創作時，與本作的開發團隊有更密切的合作，這亦使有更多的視覺元素能與音樂聯繫起來。安德森指出，小男孩呼吸時的胸部動作及聲音效果皆是源於自己呼吸時的動作及聲音，而當小男孩到達遊戲內的不同位置時，小男孩所表現出的平靜或恐慌情緒亦會影響呼吸時的胸部動作及聲音效果<ref name="JB_1" />。安德森亦在遊戲的整體結構及節奏上提供建議予遊戲設計團隊，希望自己的音樂能有助於建立遊戲內的緊張情緒<ref name="JB_1" />。

微軟在2014年6月的[[E3电子娱乐展|電子娛樂展]]新聞發布會上公布了本作<ref name="PK_1" />。在公布前，本作已被計劃在[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]及[[OS_X|OS X]]等非微軟平台上發行<ref name="AG_2" />。為了減短公布活動及發行之間的時間，Playdead曾特意等了四年<ref name="AG_1" />。[[IGN|IGN]]的瑞安·麥卡弗里表示此次公布是微軟對獨立遊戲開發的承諾的一個標誌<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/09/e3-2014-microsoft-is-all-about-the-games |title = E3 2014:Microsoft is all About the Games |author = Lucy O'Brien |date = 2014-06-09 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160812025156/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/09/e3-2014-microsoft-is-all-about-the-games |archive-date = 2016-08-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並且是他本人在這一年內的最大驚喜<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/12/24/the-biggest-surprises-of-2014 |title = The Biggest Surprises of 2014 |author = IGN's Jaw-Dropped Editors |date = 2014-12-24 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160812035229/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/12/24/the-biggest-surprises-of-2014 |archive-date = 2016-08-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。開發團隊其後將本作的發行日推遲，並希望進一步完善遊戲，但沒有提及預期的發行日期<ref name="SS_1" /><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.destructoid.com/limbo-developer-s-follow-up-inside-sees-a-delay-293369.phtml |title = Limbo developer's follow-up 'Inside' sees a delay |author = Chris Carter |date = 2015-06-05 |publisher = Destructoid |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160804213122/https://www.destructoid.com/limbo-developer-s-follow-up-inside-sees-a-delay-293369.phtml |archive-date = 2016-08-04 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在發行日推遲後，原本Playdead計劃在Xbox One及Windows平台上進行初始發行<ref name="PK_1" />，但之後表示在未來有興趣於其他平台上發行<ref name="AG_1" />。

Playdead在2016年的電子娛樂展上公布本作的發行日期，並推出限時促銷，讓玩家們在本作發行前免費下載《地獄邊境》。本作最終於2016年6月29日及7月7日在Xbox One及Windows版的[[Steam|Steam]]平台上發行<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/13/e3-2016-limbo-follow-up-inside-gets-a-release-date |title = E3 2016: Limbo Follow-Up Inside Gets a Release Date |author = Miranda Sanchez |date = 2016-06-13 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701013550/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/06/13/e3-2016-limbo-follow-up-inside-gets-a-release-date |archive-date = 2016-07-01 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。之后游戏于同年8月23日在PlayStation 4上发售。在2017年东京游戏展期间，Playdead在接受采访时表示游戏未来会登陆到[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]以及[[iOS|iOS]]上。<ref name="NSandIOS">[https://www.famitsu.com/news/201709/23142542.html 世界各国で絶賛された『INSIDE』、Nintendo Switch版、iOS版が開発中であることが判明] {{Wayback|url=https://www.famitsu.com/news/201709/23142542.html |date=20170923145954 }}.Fami通.2017-09-23.[2017-09-23].</ref>

