本作獲得普遍好評，遊戲評論網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於69條評論給予本作的Xbox One版本92/100的評價<ref name="MC_X1"/>。本作在[[Polygon|Polygon]]及[[IGN|IGN]]上均是2016年最令人期待的電子遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.polygon.com/a/2016-game-preview-100-games/ooooh-pretty |title = Games of 2016: Ooooh pretty |publisher = Polygon |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160720113749/http://www.polygon.com/a/2016-game-preview-100-games/ooooh-pretty |archive-date = 2016-07-20 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/01/01/32-games-to-keep-on-your-radar-in-2016 |title = 32 Games to Keep on Your Radar in 2016 |author = Chloi Rad |date = 2016-01-01 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160708172839/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/01/01/32-games-to-keep-on-your-radar-in-2016 |archive-date = 2016-07-08 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在2016年電子娛樂展上的遊戲預覽上，馬蒂·席爾瓦（Marty Sliva）認為本作的標題應為《超級地獄邊境》，因為Playdead以相同的方式將《地獄邊境》改進改良而造就本作，就好比[[任天堂|任天堂]]將他們的遊戲帶至[[超級任天堂|超級任天堂]]一樣<ref name="MS_1" />。

本作在電子娛樂展的遊戲評論家獎上獲得「最佳獨立遊戲」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/here-are-e3-2016s-game-critics-award-winners/1100-6441502/ |title = Here Are E3 2016's Game Critics Award Winners |author = Chris Pereira |date = 2016-07-05 |publisher = Gamespot |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://archive.is/20160710064003/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/here-are-e3-2016s-game-critics-award-winners/1100-6441502/ |archive-date = 2016-07-10 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的科克·漢密爾頓（Kirk Hamilton）表示相對於Playdead另一款遊戲《地獄邊境》的成功，本作是「進化」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://kotaku.com/inside-the-limbo-crews-new-game-is-utterly-fantastic-1781818278 |title = INSIDE: The Kotaku Review |author = Kirk Hamilton |date = 2016-06-13 |publisher = Kotaku |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160708132701/http://kotaku.com/inside-the-limbo-crews-new-game-is-utterly-fantastic-1781818278 |archive-date = 2016-07-08 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

USgamer的賈茲·雷格諾（Jaz Rignall）在預覽本作後指出本作是在他玩過的眾多解謎遊戲之中最為出色的一款，甚至比前作《地獄邊境》更為優秀<ref name="JR_1" />。

部份遊戲評論家指出本作與《地獄邊境》相比毫不遜色，甚至是《地獄邊境》當之無愧的精神續作<ref name="CD_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-06-28-inside-review |title = Inside review |author = Christian Donlan |date = 2016-06-28 |publisher = Eurogamer |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160714141122/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-06-28-inside-review |archive-date = 2016-07-14 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="MP_1">{{Cite web |url = http://time.com/4380020/inside-review/ |title = Inside review |author = Matt Peckham |date = 2016-06-28 |publisher = Time |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160703193252/http://time.com/4380020/inside-review/ |archive-date = 2016-07-03 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="CK_1">{{Cite web |url = http://www.wired.com/2016/06/inside-review/ |title = Inside review |author = Chris Kohler |date = 2016-06-28 |publisher = Wired |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160715160747/http://www.wired.com/2016/06/inside-review |archive-date = 2016-07-15 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="AW_2">{{Cite web |url = http://www.theverge.com/2016/6/28/12050342/inside-review-xbox-one-steam |title = Inside is an incredible, unsettling adventure from the creators of Limbo |author = Andrew Webster |date = 2016-06-28 |publisher = The Verge |language = en |accessdate = 2016-07-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160707074126/http://www.theverge.com/2016/6/28/12050342/inside-review-xbox-one-steam |archive-date = 2016-07-07 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

